<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" role="crossHeading" topic="statutoryNotes" id="id74a1458d-3a70-11f1-9d9e-dfac6d46cab7"><heading class="centered"><b>Statutory Notes and Related Subsidiaries</b></heading></note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="miscellaneous" id="id74a1458e-3a70-11f1-9d9e-dfac6d46cab7"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Termination of Reporting Requirements</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">For termination, effective <date date="2000-05-15">May 15, 2000</date>, of reporting provisions in this section, see <ref href="/us/pl/104/66/s3003">section 3003 of Pub. L. 104–66</ref>, set out as a note under <ref href="/us/usc/t31/s1113">section 1113 of Title 31</ref>, Money and Finance, and page 204 of House Document No. 103–7.</p>
